
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Services";
}

<div class="container body-content">
    <h4 class="text-center">Services</h4>
        <div class="row offset-md-1 my-4">
            <div class="col-md-5 thinborder rounded m-1">
                <h5 class="text-center">Airport Parking</h5>
                <p>
                    At ParkEasy Airport Parking we provide simple and easy airport parking for literally unbeatable prices. We are located just four miles from Glasgow Airport and provide a shuttle service for our customers when departing and returning to collect your vehicle.
                </p>
                <p>Our facilities include: </p>
                <p>
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> CCTV Monitoring<br>
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> 24/7 Security Staff<br>
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Controlled Entry/Exit Barriers<br>
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Full Insurance Coverage<br>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 thinborder rounded m-1">
                <h5 class="text-center">Valet Service</h5>
                <p>
                    We have also recently upgraded our parking facilities and now offer both a full and mini valet service costing either <strong class="text-darkblue">£10.00</strong> or <strong class="text-darkblue">£20.00</strong>. Vehicle valeting is carried out on-site by our professional valet staff in time for your return from your trip.
                </p>
                <div class="row">
                    <p class="col-md-6">
                        The mini valet service includes: <br><br>

                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Vehicle Wash &amp; Wax <br>
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Interior Clean <br>
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Interior Polish <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Tyre Shine <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Air Fresheners <br />
                    </p>
                    <p class="col-md-6">
                        The full valet service includes: <br><br>

                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Vehicle Wash &amp; Wax <br>
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Interior Clean <br>
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Seat Shampoo/Clean <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Interior Polish <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Tyre Shine <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Wheel Arch Jet Wash <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Air Fresheners <br />
                        <i class="fas fa-check text-darkblue"></i> Interior/Exterior Polish <br />
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <center style="padding-bottom: 30px;"><button type="submit" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Create", "Bookings")'" class="btn btn-darkblue font-weight-bold">Book with ParkEasy Today</button></center>


</div>

